### Example: Piecewise Initial Condition

Suppose we have the following piecewise initial condition:
\[ u(x, 0) = \begin{cases} 
x & \text{if } 0 \leq x \leq \frac{1}{2} \\
1 - x & \text{if } \frac{1}{2} < x \leq 1 
\end{cases} \]

We'll use the finite difference method to numerically solve the wave equation \( u_{tt} = c^2 u_{xx} \) with this initial condition and visualize the wave motion in MATLAB.

### Step-by-Step Guide

#### Step 1: Define the Wave Equation and Initial Conditions

```matlab
