% Plot the Fourier series approximation with N_terms = 20
plot(x, u_approx_20, 'g-.', 'LineWidth', 2, 'DisplayName', 'N_terms = 20');

xlabel('x');
ylabel('u(x,0)');
title('Initial Condition and Fourier Series Approximations');
legend show;
grid on;
```

